data.description: 2 bdrm, 1 bath ranch. Large LR with adjoining dining room with walkout. Updated equipped kitchen and bath. Hardwood floors throughout. Full basement with walk out to large pie shaped fenced yard. Freshly painted. Located in a cul de sac. Walking distance to schools, recreation center, restaurants, and bus stop. 12 minutes to downtown, 20 to CGV, 5 to Coney Island & Belterra. Move in ready.
